== 评价 ==

=== 演员反响 ===
《激情》一众演员起初对伊芙的人物形象和情节反响良好。约翰逊称赞节目不但包含伊芙这样的非裔角色，而且有“完整的非裔美国人家族”，不致“只是一闪而过”，这在当时的日间电视剧还不多见。约翰逊还称，非裔美国观众同样对罗素家族反响良好。<ref name="Casting3" />另据约翰逊透露，罗斯在《[[星探_(1983年电视剧)|星探]]》（''{{lang|en|Star Search}}''）亮相后一直是非裔社区有名的年轻美女，能与她合作正是自己接演罗素的重要原因<ref name="ItGirl">{{cite news | title = Chemical Reaction | last = Calega | first = Tony | date = 2000-07-25 | work = Soap Opera Weekly | publisher = Source Interlink}}</ref>。马歇尔觉得丽兹与伊芙的敌对有些荒谬，特别是两人在克兰家族庄园大打出手的情节。马歇尔认可罗斯的演出，还称自己出演的角色一直想找伊芙麻烦，但罗斯却能保持戏外关系友好，这对演员来说是很有价值的天赋，这样的演员能无所畏惧、挥洒自如地演出。<ref name="KeepingItClose">{{cite news | title = Keeping It Close | date = 2006-02-07 | work = Soap Opera Digest | publisher = American Media}}</ref>

众演员对伊芙的后期情节反响不佳。罗斯很反感伊芙与文森特打交道的情节，对文森特生下亲身父亲的儿子“恶心至极”，起初根本演不下去，直到节目表演教练玛丽亚·奥布赖恩（{{lang|en|Maria O'Brien}}）提点才鼓起勇气演完。<ref name="casting22" />节目演员[[麦肯兹·怀斯摩尔|麦肯兹·怀斯摩尔]]（{{lang|en|McKenzie Westmore}}）谴责伊芙手术时接反朱利安阴茎的情节，认为这是节目取消的重要原因：“这肯定是史上最糟剧情，真不知他们怎么想的！”<ref name="Penis">{{cite web | url = https://toofab.com/2015/07/30/passions-now-then-mckenzie-westmore/ | title = McKenzie Westmore Talks 'Face Off,' Craziest 'Passions' Moment & How 'Batman v. Superman' Changed Her Wedding Date! | date = 2015-07-31 | publisher = Too Fab | access-date = 2021-03-21 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171110142246/https://toofab.com/2015/07/30/passions-now-then-mckenzie-westmore/ | archive-date = 2017-11-10 }}</ref>

=== 专业评价 ===
电视评论员和剧迷普遍认可伊芙·罗素。《[[肥皂剧文摘|肥皂剧文摘]]》（''{{lang|en|Soap Opera Digest}}''）民意调查多次将罗斯评为《激情》剧迷最喜欢的女演员<ref name="character 4" />。《[[电视指南_(美国杂志)|电视指南]]》不但把罗斯评为肥皂剧十大美女第八位，还称她是《激情》最具天赋的女演员<ref name="TVGuideStuff">{{cite web | url = https://www.tvfanatic.com/2007/07/the-top-10-most-beautiful-soap-opera-actresses/ | title = The Top 10 Most Beautiful Soap Opera Actresses | last = Richenthal | publisher = TV Fanatic | date = 2007-07-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180622094335/https://www.tvfanatic.com/2007/07/the-top-10-most-beautiful-soap-opera-actresses/ | archive-date = 2018-06-22 | first = Matt | access-date = 2021-03-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2006年伯尔劳在采访罗斯时称，伊芙是人气很高的日间电视角色<ref name="character 4" />。《[[自由星报|自由星报]]》（''{{lang|en|The Free Lance–Star}}''）向剧迷征求《激情》情节创意，观众回复声称伊芙与艾薇的敌对情节“在我看过的日间电视节目位居首位”<ref name="EveIvyTheBestFights">{{cite web | access-date = 2021-03-21 | dead-url = no | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1298&dat=20000507&id=RwUzAAAAIBAJ&pg=3209,1739119 | title = NBC's "Passions" solves nursing shortage: monkeys can do the job! | last = Havens | first = Candace | date = 2000-05-07 | work = The Free Lance–Star  | archive-url = https://archive.is/20161121170717/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1298&dat=20000507&id=RwUzAAAAIBAJ&sjid=zQgGAAAAIBAJ&pg=3209,1739119 | archive-date = 2016-11-21 }}</ref>。

评论界普遍看好伊芙与朱利安的恋情。《电视指南》称赞两位演员的化学反响，将伊芙与朱利安列入最佳肥皂剧超级情侣<ref name=":0">{{cite web | archive-date = 2008-10-04 | dead-url = yes | work = TV Guide | url = http://entertainment1.sympatico.msn.ca/TV_Guide/Soaps/Features/Articles/071018_supercouples_passions_NB | title = Soaps' best super-couples! | last = Branco | first = Nelson | publisher = [[CBS公司|CBS Corporation]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081004105125/http://entertainment1.sympatico.msn.ca/TV_Guide/Soaps/Features/Articles/071018_supercouples_passions_NB | access-date = 2021-03-21 }}</ref>，《[[肥皂剧周刊|肥皂剧周刊]]》（{{lang|en|''Soap Opera Weekly''}}）把两人称为“《激情》扭计冤家”<ref name="Name2">{{cite news | title = The Odd Couple of Passions | date = 2002-10-29 | work = Soap Opera Weekly | publisher = Source Interlink}}</ref>。剧迷也喜欢两人的恋情并创造[[混成詞|混成詞]]“伊芙安”（{{lang|en|Evian}}）<ref name="Reception5">{{cite news | title = Somethings in the 'Evian' | last = Barnert | first = Deanna | year = 2004 | work = Soap Opera Weekly | publisher = Source Interlink}}</ref>。据罗斯透露，《激情》没有因关注异族恋情侣招来非议<ref name="onthefly">{{cite news | title = On The Floy with Passions' Tracey Ross 11 questions in 11 minutes | last = Barnert | first = Deanna | date = 2004-05 | work = Soap Opera Weekly | publisher = Source Interlink}}</ref>。她曾在接受《肥皂剧周刊》采访时表示，无论是伊芙与朱利安在一起，还是她在现实生活中与扮演朱利安的[[本·马斯特斯|本·马斯特斯]]（{{lang|en|Ben Masters}}）交往，估计都会引来种族主义者批判<ref name="NoThrowingRocks">{{cite news | title = Reality Check | date = 2003-04 | work = Soap Opera Weekly | publisher = Source Interlink}}</ref>。不过，“Soapdom.com”网站刊登莱斯利安·科克（{{lang|en|Lesleyann Coker}}）的评论指出，这段恋情令朱利安的为人改变，他本来酗酒且对伴侣不忠，但受伊芙影响变得“温柔、软弱、仿佛失去灵魂”<ref name="Louse">{{cite web | archive-date = 2017-01-04 | access-date = 2017-01-14 | url = http://www.soapdom.com/Busted-to-Blissful/october-2004-passions.html | title = October 2004 ~ Passions | last = Coker | first = Lesleyann | date = 2004-10-07 | publisher = Soapdom.com | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170104104905/http://www.soapdom.com/Busted-to-Blissful/october-2004-passions.html }}</ref>。

罗斯因出演伊芙八次获[[有色人种进步协会形象奖|有色人种进步协会形象奖]][[有色人种进步协会形象奖最佳剧情类日间电视剧女主角|最佳剧情类日间电视剧女主角]]提名，并在[[第38届有色人种进步协会形象奖|2007年]]胜出<ref name="character 4" /><ref name="Awards1">{{cite web | archive-date = 2021-03-14 | access-date = 2021-03-21 | dead-url = no | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2007-03-03-naacp-winners-list_N.htm | title = 38th annual NAACP Image Awards winners | work = [[今日美國|USA Today]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210314175049/https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2007-03-03-naacp-winners-list_N.htm }}</ref>。《[[Jet_(杂志)|Jet]]》杂志发文称赞伊芙等人组成的罗素家族“混然一体”，而不是装点门面的符号<ref name="Casting3" />。

